{"tid":1990421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國政府信件：中國曾游說冀德方稱讚北京抗疫工作","createTime":"2020-04-26T16:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T02:41:41.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"624986e90724182c9936401ccc366457739830fc","tid":1990421,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"德國政府信件：中國曾游說冀德方稱讚北京抗疫工作<br />\n26.04.2020 23:52<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，德國內政部日前去信綠黨一名國會議員，回覆對方查詢，指知悉曾有個別中國外交人員接觸德國官員，希望促成德方就中國應對新型冠狀病毒疫情發表正面的公開聲明，但聯邦政府未有按照這些要求行事。當地《周日世界報》引述中國駐柏林大使館駁斥報道，指報道不實及不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，德國內政部在信中提到，即使中方不提出要求，德方亦認為中國自1月23日以來已致力控制疫情，並已告知中國政府，透明及公開對抗疫非常重要，但未有說明是否認為中方已做到這點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283516&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283516%26csid%3D261_341&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4MjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=68255fe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283516&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6e8899d2d0e05fafe8d993669e0f9f7789ba4f4e","tid":1990421,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0GEMNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0GEMNb.jpg&h=b496f223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8be2e338dc05d33c18539096f0195badea879eea","tid":1990421,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾，最後咪又係奶共<br />\n肯定中方"},{"pid":"5c31f08f6afdf0eabd6e8b3a1402a4ad335494ce","tid":1990421,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"OLD NEWS?"},{"pid":"0ead0056a8f05894b756ede9972348f54ee62d60","tid":1990421,"uid":55496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T16:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\"